ollapse\">\n                    <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav navbar-right\">\n                        <!-- ADD MENU LINKS HERE. THESE ARE NON-FUNCTIONAL EXAMPLES. -->\n                        <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\">Our Store</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/usr/dealsonlywebstore\">About Us</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://contact.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?ContactUserNextGen&amp;recipient=dealsonlywebstore\">Contact Us</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <div>\n                    <div class=\"main-image\">\n                        <img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/73359/8VCWhwKTh7u2ZOGy3yzrwxniWIjK8N-metaYmVlY2h3b29kX3BhcmVudC5qcGc=-.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Responsive image\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <h3>Product Details</h3>\n                <!-- ADD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR YOU CAN REMOVE THE TABLE COMPLETELY-->\n                <div class=\"product-specs\">\n                    <table><tbody>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SILICONE KITCHEN UTENSILS SET: Featuring sturdy beech wood handles,100% food grade silicone and heat resistant up to 400F, these highly durable neutral colored silicone kitchen utensils are a stylish and modern addition to any kitchen!</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DISHWASHER SAFE: After cooking, baking or meal and food prep, toss any of these silicone kitchens on the top rack for quick and easy clean up; stain and odor resistant, make that homemade Bolognese spaghetti sauce or tomato bisque without worry!</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">BPA FREE KITCHEN UTENSILS: This silicone cooking spoon, as well as all kitchen utensils in this collection, are of food grade quality and BPA free, making them a safe and reliable choice for cooking and baking; hygienic, hypoallergenic and constructed with no open pores to harbor bacteria</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">BEECH WOOD HANDLES: The solid cooking silicone spoon features easy to grip durable handles made of sturdy beech wood; the silicone spoon features a built in handle hole design for easy hanging storage or display if preferred</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS: 13.5 x 2.75 x 1.5 inches approximately, varies by style</td>\n                            </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h1>Beille Beech Wood and Silicone Kitchen Utensils Cooking Baking Supplies Home Essentials, Light Grey</h1>\n                <h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">49.99</span></h2>\n                <p>The contending heroes of any kitchen? Reliable, silicone kitchen utensils say us! From scrambling eggs, sauteing vegetables and flipping quesadillas, to scraping out brownie batter or removing delicate won tons, we reach for these silicone kitchen utensils time and time again in the kitchen, and for good reason.\n\nAll the kitchen utensils included in this collection from Beille feature high quality BPA free food grade silicone, are dishwasher and freezer safe, odor resistant, stain resistant and heat resistant up to 400F, and all come with sturdy and durable beech wood handles.\n\nEasy and comfortable to maneuver, the kitchen utensils measure approximately 13.5 inches in length, providing excellent control and a comfortable grip over whatever recipe you’re taking on next! The kitchen tools or kitchen gadgets features a matte silicone finish in a stylish light grey colorway, while each kitchen utensil comes with a top handle hole design if hanging storage or display is preferred. And, importantly, these silicone cooking utensil set won’t scratch or mark pots and pans like other utensils can, especially where ceramic and nonstick cookware or bake ware are concerned.\n\nThe notable versatility, durability and high heat resistance of this Beille silicone and beech wood kitchen utensils collection makes a great investment for any kitchen, and an absolute home essentials item for any baker, professional chef or home cook!</p>\n                <div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n                    <div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-100\">\n                        <p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n                        <p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n                        <a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n     